result.notes:
Gridded data, in ascii text format, of wind turbines at the spatial extent of 
the North Sea (2015-2016). Data are produced at three different spatial 
resolutions: 0.1, 0.25 and 0.5 decimal degree, respectively. Values represent 
estimated proportion of grid cell occupied by structures.

Data were derived as model inputs to support two Cefas projects ( **COSM** 
and ** EcoConnect** ) under the ** INSITE** (INfluence of man-made 
Structures In The Ecosystem) programme.
